      "body" : "The OSValidator class supports OSX, but the getNumberOfCores completely ignores it. As an aside, <a href=\"https://blog.opengroup.org/2015/10/02/mac-os-x-el-capitan-achieves-unix-certification/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">blog.opengroup.org/2015/10/02/&hellip;</a>    so &#39;Mac&#39; should be in your isUnix() but... For BSD, OSX, no lscpu command exists and your getNumberOfCores will return 0."
