    "body" : "<p>If you want to dubbel check the amount of cores you have on your machine to the number your java program is giving you.</p>\n<p>In Linux terminal: <code>lscpu</code></p>\n<p>In Windows terminal (cmd): <code>echo %NUMBER_OF_PROCESSORS%</code></p>\n<p>In Mac terminal: <code>sysctl -n hw.ncpu</code></p>\n"
